\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 His stats and resource pools had increased quite a bit from the beginning of the process and his skills list had expanded tremendously. He also figured that his title list was probably pretty good. Seven titles with around three days remaining in the introduction seemed pretty good.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Your progress has been quite impressive so far,\u8221\'94 the Guide stated as he closed his status screen. \u8220\'93Your performance thus far is likely to unlock some interesting paths for you, especially if you perform this well in the final evaluation.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93I assume the next set of evaluations will focus on mental attributes?\u8221\'94 He was pretty sure he knew the answer, but it never hurt to verify.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Essentially yes,\u8221\'94 she replied. \u8220\'93It will put you through a series of tests and trials meant to instill some skills that will improve your mental stats as they develop. While these trials will be considerably longer than any of the previous evaluations, they will be far less physically demanding for the most part.\u8221\'94 The Guide tilted her head as she considered him again. \u8220\'93You will, however want to recoup your mana and stamina as you will need mana for the first evaluation cycle.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Marcus nodded and began meditating to restore his mana and stamina. }
