\par\pard\plain \tx0\tx360\tx720\tx1080\tx1440\tx1800\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\fi360\ltrch\loch \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Marcus submerged himself deeply into his meditation, losing himself in the mana flowing within his body. He shut off all of his notifications and just focused. While he knew time was passing, he was almost completely unaware of it. He felt the notifications building up as his meditation skill leveled and he could watch his mana core refill. It took more than three hours to completely refill his mana pool, which regenerated much more slowly than stamina. Even with his mana core refilled, he continued to focus on refining his meditation skills. After quite a few hours, he exited meditation and opened his last few notifications.}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
