\par\plain {\f1\fs24\b0\i0 Congratulations! Journeyman Mana Control (Tier 5) has improved to Level 5!}
\par\plain {\f1\fs24\b0\i0 Congratulations! Basic Meditation (Tier 2) has improved to Level 28! <!$Scr_Ps::0>}
\par\pard\plain \tx0\tx360\tx720\tx1080\tx1440\tx1800\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\fi360\ltrch\loch \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 With his mana pool refilled, he shifted his focus to another goal he had wanted to pursue, attempting to create a magic spell. He began by considering how the staff he had used during the dexterity evaluation had converted his mana into a destructive bolt. He had spent two full hours using the implement and becoming familiar with the construct within the staff. With concentration and focus, he began to gather up some mana and manipulate it the way the staff had. It took a long time for Marcus to figure out how to shape the mana correctly, but once he started to make progress it sped up quickly. As a crackling bolt of destructive energy coalesced above his hand, he received another System notification.}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\pard\plain \tx0\tx360\tx720\tx1080\tx1440\tx1800\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\fi360\ltrch\loch {\f1\fs24\b0\i0 <$Scr_Ps::0>Congratulations! Skill learned: Beginner Unguided Mana Bolt (Tier 1) Level 1! Wisdom has increased by 1!}
