\par\plain {\f1\fs24\b0\i0 You have gained the title \loch\af1\hich\af1\dbch\af1\uc1\u8216\'91Spellcrafting Prodigy\u8217\'92.  All spells and abilities you create are improved by 10% in power and efficiency.}
